            "rating": "shopify://shop_images/Empire_Rating.svg",
            "content": "<p>“I’ve had the pleasure of working with Cook & Bathe for close to 10 years. The team is professional, responsive, and brings a depth of knowledge in their field. They take the time to understand their clients’ needs and consistently deliver high-quality kitchen, bathroom, and laundry fixtures that meet both aesthetic and functional requirements.”</p>",
